Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.15,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,宿醉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:11.88,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,萊利娜大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:14.37,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,貝妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:18.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我今天還想再睡一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.63,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有客人找您  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:22.42,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:26.42,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就說我身體不舒服讓人回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:29.14,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,前來光臨的是溫奈特公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:32.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:37.38,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,交易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是關於玉璽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,老爺和夫人都出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:46.26,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,您打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:48.96,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:50.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你讓他在客廳等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:57.51,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我得好好告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:00:59.67,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,告訴他  如果不想暴露自己的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:02.87,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就跟我聯手  幫忙把這樁婚約解除
